data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This spacious four-bedroom, 2.5-bath house features a large living room, dining room, updated kitchen, and generous family room to enjoy family and friends. Step out onto the large deck in the fully fenced-in back yard to enjoy  summer bbq's with family and friends. The primary suite has a large walk-in closet and a private, remodeled bath with a large soaking tub to relax after a long day. The basement is finished and includes a laundry room and additional storage. Many updates have been done, so you can just move in and enjoy! Plus, you're close to shopping, restaurants, and all that Pickerington has to offer.
